data.description: Welcome home to paradise!!  This cottage style home has tons of charm with its large front porch that has views of the wetland preserve.  As you enter through the front door you are greeted with 10 foot ceilings, hardwood floors and a wide-open floor plan.  The kitchen appliances are stainless steel, and the refrigerator and dishwasher will remain.  There are tons of kitchen cabinets and a custom wood hood over the gas cooktop. There is also a large pantry, separate coffee station and island with counter height seating.  There is a half bath off the kitchen as well as a spot for a home management area.  There is a large laundry room outside the master bedroom for easy access.  The master bedroom is a generous size and the master bath has double vanities, separate shower, garden tub and large walk-in closet.  Upstairs there are three bedrooms with one that has an ensuite bathroom.  There is another bathroom that serves the other bedrooms.  There is also great closet space and more storage!!  Outside there is a two-car carport with covered access and outside storage. There is also under the house storage for lawn equipment and seasonal decor.  This is a very energy efficient house including high efficiency heat pumps, tankless water heater, upgraded insulation, security system and sprinkler system!!  The Waters offers a laid-back lifestyle with plenty of amenities to enjoy.    That includes swimming pools, tennis courts, playgrounds, parks and a huge lake!!  Don't miss this one!
